{"synckey":1673277791,"updated":[{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_135_1159-1243","chapterUid":135,"markText":"牢记投资者在经济低迷时期可能会哄抬生活消费品股票的股价，使得股票价格相对于它的公平价值高很多。当生活消费品行业的股票有20%~30%的安全边际交易时，可寻找买入的机会。","range":"1159-1243","createTime":1651404856,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_131_1895-1973","chapterUid":131,"markText":"增长最快的生活消费品公司（不管这种增长是源于创新还是收购）也不可能大幅度超越整体经济的增长，因为盈利的增长必须更多地依赖经营结构的改进而不是营业收入的增长。","range":"1895-1973","createTime":1651289816,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_7_467-532","chapterUid":7,"markText":"是什么把一家坏公司与好公司区分开来的呢？在很大程度上，这取决于一家公司自身竞争优势的大小。竞争优势可以用来保护企业的利益免受侵害。","range":"467-532","createTime":1599657825,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_22_1379-1439","chapterUid":22,"markText":"行业内的公司是怎样和其他公司竞争的呢？这是一个很有利可图的、有吸引力的行业，还是一个参与者都在痛苦挣扎的过度竞争的行业？","range":"1379-1439","createTime":1582713361,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_22_1277-1305","chapterUid":22,"markText":"评估一家公司能阻挡竞争者多久，这是该公司竞争优势的周期。","range":"1277-1305","createTime":1582713349,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_22_1215-1244","chapterUid":22,"markText":"为什么这家公司能阻挡竞争者，是什么阻止竞争者窃取它的利润？","range":"1215-1244","createTime":1582713328,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_22_1092-1117","chapterUid":22,"markText":"这家公司的资产和所有者权益一直能够创造稳定收益吗？","range":"1092-1117","createTime":1582713317,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_26_1125-1152","chapterUid":26,"markText":"竞争优势能帮助一家好公司继续保持已经取得的地位和优势。","range":"1125-1152","createTime":1582713212,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_26_1182-1240","chapterUid":26,"markText":"寻找持续高盈利的公司，这是公司拥有竞争优势的证据。你可以关注自由现金流、净利润、净资产收益率和资产收益率等度量指标。","range":"1182-1240","createTime":1582713203,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_26_1399-1444","chapterUid":26,"markText":"用两个维度思考竞争优势：深度（公司能赚多少钱）和宽度（能保持平均水平以上的利润多长时间）。","range":"1399-1444","createTime":1582713174,"type":1},{"bookId":"934451","bookmarkId":"934451_26_1543-1559","chapterUid":26,"markText":"一些行业就是比其他行业赚钱容易。","range":"1543-1559","createTime":1582713166,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"结论","chapterUid":135,"chapterIdx":135},{"title":"行业分析","chapterUid":26,"chapterIdx":26},{"title":"第三章 竞争优势","chapterUid":22,"chapterIdx":22},{"title":"寻找具有强大竞争优势的公司","chapterUid":7,"chapterIdx":7},{"title":"成长的重要策略","chapterUid":131,"chapterIdx":131}],"book":{"bookId":"934451","version":1270858251,"format":"epub","soldout":1,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://wfqqreader-1252317822.image.myqcloud.com/cover/451/934451/s_934451.jpg","title":"股市真规则（畅销版）","author":"帕特·多尔西","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"K9Q4Mqwd{gNbj@xFE3oLxs","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#370e14"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#400211"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#48000f"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#4d2523"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#571e1c"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#611116"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#683b34"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#74352b"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#7f2c21"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#920807"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8f4e41"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a53f2a"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#82544b"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#c35a3f"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#9b6f64"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b7624c"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b6897d"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#c48372"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#d27d66"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#eb6e4a"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#ef977d"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#fc9071"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff8861"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#ecbdb0"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#fdb7a3"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ffa176"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#f2dfd9"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffbb91"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#d27d66"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#ef977d"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#270500"}],"dominate_color":{"hex":"#e3420b","hsv":[15.293473657076709,95.1259454821464,88.98954524453832]},"custom_cover":"https://weread-1258476243.file.myqcloud.com/bookalphacover/451/934451/s_934451.jpg","custom_rec_cover":"https://weread-1258476243.file.myqcloud.com/bookreccover/451/934451/s_934451.jpg","colorsPure":["#eb6e4a","#ff